title: Ripout - Official Release Date Announcement | Realms Deep 2023
description:
Ripout is an online first-person co-op shooter developed by Pet Project Games. Players must fight against mutant monsters in procedurally generated levels by collecting loot, customizing their character, and trusting their Pet Gun companion. Ripout is launching into Early Access on October 24 for PC.

#Ripout

title: On Air - Official Teaser Trailer #3 | Realms Deep 2023
description:
On Air is a sci-fi visual novel survival horror game developed by RainStyle games. Players will wake up in a strange place with creatures hiding in the dark trying to kill anything that crosses its path. Encountering an unknown mechanism is the only way to make it out alive. On Air is launching soon for PC.

#OnAir

title: They Are Here: Alien Abduction Horror - Official Prologue Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
description:
They Are Here: Alien Abduction Horror is a first-person alien abduction horror game developed by Deklazon. Players will take up the role of a journalist who has witnessed a real and true alien abduction at a local farm. Explore where the alien craft landed, take photos for analysis, and seek the truth. They Are Here: Alien Abduction is launching in 2024 for PC.

#TheyAreHereAlienAbductionHorror

title: Winnie's Hole - Official Announcement Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
description:
Winnie's Hole is a 2D strategy dungeon crawler roguelite RPG developed by Twice Different. Players will embody a virus within Winnie's body tasked with capturing cells to grow more limbs and overtake Winnie the Pooh. Winnie's Hole is launching in 2023 for PC.

#WinniesHole

title: Warpath X Metal Slug 3 - Official Crossover Trailer
description:
Warpath is a mobile free-to-play competitive real-time strategy game developed by Lilith Games. A new collaboration has been unveiled bringing iconic characters to a new battlefield from Metal Slug 3. Franchise icons Marco Rossi and Eri Kasamoto are now accessible as playable characters for Warpath alongside new combat missions, special vehicles, and a special event to win cash rewards. The Warpath X Metal Slug 3 collaboration event for Warpath is available now for iOS, Android, and PC.
